data.description: Move in ready 3 bedroom 2.5 bath spacious townhome. This charming home offers brand new carpet and fresh neutral paint throughout. Bright open family room has sliding glass doors that lead out to the fully screened back porch. The primary bedroom will serve as your private oasis. featuring an expansive closet and an en suite bathroom. Loft area upstairs that can be utilized as an in home office or playroom. HOA fees to include roof, exterior building maintenance, termite bond and lawn care. Centrally located off 9A and minutes from River City Marketplace and Jacksonville Airport.
